description:
Two first-year middle school girls named http://anidb.net/ch93352 [Momoyama Mirai] and http://anidb.net/ch93353 [Moegi Emo] are aspiring idols who decide to use the "Pri☆Chan System," a system used by famous people and companies to broadcast content. Like many girls starting their own channels and uploading content, the pair decide to become their own producers, starting their own channel in an attempt to become Pri☆Chan idols.
Source: ANN
